    <title>博客搭建记录</title>
    <url>/2023/01/19/bo-ke-da-jian-ji-lu/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="搭建需求"><a href="#搭建需求" class="headerlink" title="搭建需求"></a>搭建需求</h1><ul>
<li>能用的大脑</li>
<li>能用的设备（包括Android）<span id="more"></span></li>
</ul>
<h1 id="环境依赖"><a href="#环境依赖" class="headerlink" title="环境依赖"></a>环境依赖</h1><p>安装nodejs，npm，yarn，必要时需要make automake autoconf等编译工具<br>本人采用Termux（Android）</p>
<h1 id="流程"><a href="#流程" class="headerlink" title="流程"></a>流程</h1><p>! <strong>请务必确保可以连接网络</strong></p>
<h3 id="安装"><a href="#安装" class="headerlink" title="安装"></a>安装</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yarn global add hexo-cli</span><br><span class="line">hexo init blog <span class="comment"># 此过程需要连接到GitHub仓库，请确保网络畅通</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> blog</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="主题"><a href="#主题" class="headerlink" title="主题"></a>主题</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yarn add hexo-theme-keep</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>(采用本博客所用主题)</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cp</span> node_modules/hexo-theme-keep/_config.yml _config.keep.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>主题配置文件即为<code>_config.keep.yml</code>，配置项请参见主题文档</p>
<h3 id="插件"><a href="#插件" class="headerlink" title="插件"></a>插件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">yarn add hexo-clean-css  <span class="comment"># css压缩</span></span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-generator-feed <span class="comment"># rss订阅</span></span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-generator-json-content <span class="comment">#json搜索</span></span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-generator-searchdb <span class="comment"># 搜索数据库</span></span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-html-minifier <span class="comment"># html压缩</span></span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-permalink-pinyin <span class="comment"># 博客文件名转为拼音</span></span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-uglify <span class="comment"># js压缩</span></span><br><span class="line">yarn add hexo-wordcount <span class="comment"># 博文长度统计</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>配置文件<code>_config.yml</code></p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">permalink_pinyin:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">separator:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;-&#x27;</span> <span class="comment"># default: &#x27;-&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">html_minifier:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">collapseBooleanAttributes:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">collapseWhitespace:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Ignore &#x27;&lt;!-- more --&gt;&#x27; https://hexo.io/docs/tag-plugins#Post-Excerpt</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">ignoreCustomComments:</span> [ <span class="type">!!js/regexp</span> <span class="string">/^\s*more/</span>]</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">removeComments:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">removeEmptyAttributes:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">removeScriptTypeAttributes:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">removeStyleLinkTypeAttributes:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">minifyJS:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">minifyCSS:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">clean_css:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">exclude:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;*.min.css&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">uglify:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">mangle:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">output:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">compress:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">exclude:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&#x27;*.min.js&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="基本配置"><a href="#基本配置" class="headerlink" title="基本配置"></a>基本配置</h3><p><code>_config.yml</code></p>
<p>Site区：</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Site</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">title:</span> <span class="string">博客标题</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">subtitle:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;副标题&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">description:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;描述（seo）&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">keywords:</span> <span class="string">关键字</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">author:</span> <span class="string">作者</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">language:</span> <span class="string">zh-CN</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">timezone:</span> <span class="string">&#x27;Aisa/Shanghai&#x27;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>URL区：</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># URL</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">url:</span> <span class="string">博客地址(例如：https://example.com)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">pretty_urls:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">trailing_index:</span> <span class="literal">false</span> <span class="comment"># 美化url地址</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="博客配置完成"><a href="#博客配置完成" class="headerlink" title="博客配置完成"></a>博客配置完成</h3><hr>
<h1 id="部署"><a href="#部署" class="headerlink" title="部署"></a>部署</h1><p>可选GitHub Pages和Cloudflare Pages，如有自己域名，推荐Cloudflare Pages<br>这两个部署方式均需要GitHub</p>
<h1 id="流程-1"><a href="#流程-1" class="headerlink" title="流程"></a>流程</h1><h3 id="创建私有库"><a href="#创建私有库" class="headerlink" title="创建私有库"></a>创建私有库</h3><p><a class="link"   href="https://github.com/new" >创建链接<i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i></a><br>仓库名任选<br>勾选Private</p>
<h3 id="GitHub-Pages部署方式"><a href="#GitHub-Pages部署方式" class="headerlink" title="GitHub Pages部署方式"></a>GitHub Pages部署方式</h3><h4 id="生成GitHub-Token"><a href="#生成GitHub-Token" class="headerlink" title="生成GitHub Token"></a>生成GitHub Token</h4><p>打开 <code>https://github.com/settings/tokens</code></p>
<h4 id="私有库设置"><a href="#私有库设置" class="headerlink" title="私有库设置"></a>私有库设置</h4><p>打开创建私有库的设置<br><code>https://github.com/GitHub用户名/你创建的私有库名/settings/secrets/actions</code><br>添加密钥<code>HEXO_DEPLOY</code>，值为你的刚刚生成的Token</p>
<h4 id="创建公开库"><a href="#创建公开库" class="headerlink" title="创建公开库"></a>创建公开库</h4><p>库名:<code>修改为自己GitHub用户名.github.io</code></p>
<h4 id="部署自动流程"><a href="#部署自动流程" class="headerlink" title="部署自动流程"></a>部署自动流程</h4><p>打开本地博客目录，新建<code>.github/workflows</code>目录，创建并编辑<code>.github/workflows/hexo-deploy.yml</code></p>
<p>内容：</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">deploying</span> <span class="string">Hexo</span> <span class="string">project</span> <span class="string">to</span> <span class="string">GitHub</span> <span class="string">pages</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">on:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">push:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">branches:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">main</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">jobs:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">build-and-deploy:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">runs-on:</span> <span class="string">ubuntu-latest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">steps:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Checkout</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">actions/checkout@master</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="attr">name:</span> <span class="string">Build</span> <span class="string">and</span> <span class="string">Deploy</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">uses:</span> <span class="string">theme-keep/hexo-deploy-github-pages-action@master</span> <span class="comment"># 使用专门部署 Hexo 到 GitHub pages 的 action</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="attr">env:</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">PERSONAL_TOKEN:</span> <span class="string">$&#123;&#123;</span> <span class="string">secrets.HEXO_DEPLOY</span> <span class="string">&#125;&#125;</span> <span class="comment"># secret 名</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">PUBLISH_REPOSITORY:</span> <span class="string">修改为自己GitHub用户名/修改为自己GitHub</span> <span class="string">用户名.github.io</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">BRANCH:</span> <span class="string">gh-pages</span></span><br><span class="line">          <span class="attr">PUBLISH_DIR:</span> <span class="string">./public</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h4 id="完成部署"><a href="#完成部署" class="headerlink" title="完成部署"></a>完成部署</h4><p>打开本地博客目录</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line">git remote add origin git@github.com:用户名/私有库名.git</span><br><span class="line">git branch -M main</span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m <span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git push</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h2 id="等待2分钟左右，访问用户名-github-io即可"><a href="#等待2分钟左右，访问用户名-github-io即可" class="headerlink" title="等待2分钟左右，访问用户名.github.io即可"></a>等待2分钟左右，访问<code>用户名.github.io</code>即可</h2><h3 id="Cloudflare-Pages部署方式"><a href="#Cloudflare-Pages部署方式" class="headerlink" title="Cloudflare Pages部署方式"></a>Cloudflare Pages部署方式</h3><p>注册账户，进入控制台，打开Pages页面<br>连接到GitHub，登录账户，在GitHub 中选择生效的库为你创建的私有库<br>部署命令填为：hexo generate<br>环境变量添加：<br><code>NODE_VERSION</code> 值 <code>16.18.1</code><br><code>PYTHON_VERSION</code> 值 <code>3.7</code></p>
<p>打开本地博客目录</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line">git remote add origin git@github.com:用户名/私有库名.git</span><br><span class="line">git branch -M main</span><br><span class="line">git add .</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m <span class="string">&quot;hello world&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">git push</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>等待2分钟左右打开Cloudflare给出站点查看效果<br><img  
                     lazyload
                     alt="image"
                     data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/2x-ercha/twikoo-magic@master/image/huaji/huaji22.jpg"
                     
                ></p>
]]></content>
